## 8. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Groq rate limits hit during demo | Demo fails | Automatic fallback to Ollama; cache popular queries in Redis |
| Qdrant free tier suspended | Can't query vectors | Docker Qdrant locally; health-check cron to keep cloud alive |
| Supabase pauses from inactivity | DB offline | Health-check cron; easy one-click restart |
| Render cold starts (30-60s) | Slow first request | Cron job pings services every 14 minutes; show loading skeleton |
| Embedding model too slow on CPU | Ingestion takes too long | Use lightweight `nomic-embed-code-v1` (768d); batch embed in groups of 32 |
| RAGAS needs OpenAI by default | Costs money | Configure with Ollama/Groq as evaluator LLM — fully documented approach |

